lzh_formatted:
  title: 題茂珍客舍
  author: 崔元祐
  language: lzh
  text: 脩竹家家翡翠啼。雨催寒食水生溪。蒼苔小草官橋路。怕見殘紅入馬蹄。
korean:
  title: 제무진객사
  author: 최원우
  language: kor
  text: |-
    대수풀 집집마다 비취가 우는데
    비는 한식을 재촉해 시내에 물이 나네
    푸른 이끼와 잔 풀이 돋은 관교의 길에
    쇠잔한 꽃이 말발굽에 들어가는 것을 볼까 두려워한다
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0240_010_0520&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: On the Guest House of Mao Zhen
  author: Choi Won-woo
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Graceful bamboo groves—in every home the jade-green orioles sing.
    Rain urges on the cold feast season, swelling waters in the creek.
    Across the official bridge, blue moss and tender grass take root,
    And I fear to see the fading blossoms trampled beneath the horse's hooves.
  footnotes:
    - The 'cold feast season' (한식) refers to the traditional Korean observance around early spring when visits to ancestral graves occur.
    - The official bridge and the imagery of decay suggest a meditation on transience and the cyclical nature of seasons and life.
